[
  {
    "ts": "1799055025.000000",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Joyce. You still doing Tuesdays at Rosie's with Eddie? Haven't been to that place in years.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055086.000001",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U002RAY",
    "text": "Every week. This morning he was forty minutes late and still beat me to the sausage gravy.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055147.000002",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Classic Eddie. How's he doing?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055208.000003",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U002RAY",
    "text": "Fine. Talking too much. Nothing's changed since the firehouse, including the stories.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055269.000004",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "I miss that place. They still have that corner booth in the back?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055330.000005",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U002RAY",
    "text": "They moved it. Put in a pastry display. Nobody asked.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055391.000006",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Ha. What did Eddie say about that?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799055452.000007",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U002RAY",
    "text": "Nothing printable. We sat by the window. Gravy was fine.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799136765.000008",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Cleaning out the back of the garage. Found an old department photo from '98 — the Engine 7 crew. You're in it, looking about twelve years old.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799136826.000009",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U003GRANT",
    "text": "Ha. Don't throw that out. Where'd you even find it?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799136887.000010",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Under a box of Nicole's old stuff that's been in here since the wedding. Don't ask.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799136948.000011",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U003GRANT",
    "text": "Man. Who else is in it? Big Sal?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799137009.000012",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Sal, Kowalski, me. You. Couple guys I can't name anymore. My memory's fine, don't start.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799137070.000013",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U003GRANT",
    "text": "I want a copy. Can you just take a picture of it?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799137131.000014",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "I took one. Sending it now. Gloria's at garden club so I had to figure out the flash myself. It's a little crooked.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1799137192.000015",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U003GRANT",
    "text": "That's good enough. This is going on my wall.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798869864.000016",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Eddie Wojcik ordered the exact same thing he's ordered every Tuesday for six years. Scrambled eggs, wheat toast, black coffee. Asked the waitress her name. She's worked at Rosie's since before I retired.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798869925.000017",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U004HANNAH",
    "text": "lol does she not know him by now??",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798869986.000018",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "She knows him. She just plays along. We're all playing along at this point.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798870047.000019",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U004HANNAH",
    "text": "ok that's lowkey sweet tbh",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798870108.000020",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Don't tell Eddie. He'll get emotional and then I have to sit there and watch that happen.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798870169.000021",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U004HANNAH",
    "text": "haha you make it sound terrible but you show up every week 😂",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798870230.000022",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Millvale doesn't have that many diners. Options are limited.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798870291.000023",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U004HANNAH",
    "text": "fair enough 😭 same time next week I assume?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798786917.000024",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Eddie told me you're tearing apart your old workbench. Said you were going on about it at Rosie's yesterday. That true or is Eddie being Eddie?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798786978.000025",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U005BOBBY",
    "text": "I mentioned it once. Eddie turns everything into a TED talk. Pulled the lumber this morning. Gloria's at garden club so the garage is mine till four.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798787039.000026",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "You need a hand or are you doing the suffer-alone thing?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798787040.000027",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U005BOBBY",
    "text": "I'm fine. Come if you want. Don't expect lunch.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798787101.000028",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Nothing I can't move. Eleven work?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798787162.000029",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U005BOBBY",
    "text": "Eleven-thirty. Still doing the walk with Gloria. She doesn't like me cutting it short.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798787223.000030",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA",
    "text": "Got it. Bring anything?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
    "ts": "1798787284.000031",
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "user_id": "U005BOBBY",
    "text": "Just yourself. Park on the street, not the driveway.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "reply_count": "0",
    "reactions": "0"
  },
  {
